clampGt(uint256,uint256).notice: clamps a to be greater than b

clampGt(uint256,uint256,bool).notice: clamps a to be greater than b

clampGte(uint256,uint256).notice: clamps a to be greater than or equal to b

clampGte(uint256,uint256,bool).notice: clamps a to be greater than or equal to b

clampLt(uint256,uint256).notice: clamps a to be less than b

clampLt(uint256,uint256,bool).notice: clamps a to be less than b

clampLte(uint256,uint256).notice: clamps a to be less than or equal to b

clampLte(uint256,uint256,bool).notice: clamps a to be less than or equal to b

gt(uint256,uint256,string).notice: asserts that a is greater than b. Violations are logged using reason.

gte(uint256,uint256,string).notice: asserts that a is greater than or equal to b. Violations are logged using reason.

lt(uint256,uint256,string).notice: asserts that a is less than b. Violations are logged using reason.

lte(uint256,uint256,string).notice: asserts that a is less than or equal to b. Violations are logged using reason.

neq(uint256,uint256,string).notice: asserts that a is not equal to b. Violations are logged using reason.
